"# service kdc start\n"
"# service kadmind start\n"
msgstr ""
"# service kdc start\n"
"# service kadmind start\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/security/_index.adoc:919
msgid ""
"While there will not be any kerberized daemons running at this point, it is "
"possible to confirm that the KDC is functioning by obtaining a ticket for "
"the principal that was just created:"
msgstr ""
"이 시점에서 실행 중인 케르베로스화된 데몬은 없지만 방금 생성한 주체에 대한 티"
"켓을 가져와서 KDC가 작동 중인지 확인할 수 있습니다:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/security/_index.adoc:924
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"% kinit tillman\n"
"tillman@EXAMPLE.ORG's Password:\n"
msgstr ""
"% kinit tillman\n"
"tillman@EXAMPLE.ORG's Password:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/security/_index.adoc:927
